tossup_question: 28) PHYSICS  Which of the following is the most common method of producing alternating current?
tossup_MCQoptions:
W) Circuits varying from parallel to series
X) Switches automatically turning on and off 
Y) Turbines rotating backwards and forwards 
Z) Magnets spinning in a coil of wire
tossup_answer: ANSWER: Z) Magnets spinning in a coil of wire
